    <item>
      <title>土耳其的“正统”支点使里拉成为汇丰银行的最爱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/turkey-s-orthodox-pivot-makes-lira-a-favorite-for-hsbc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其回归更传统的货币政策方式正在提振投资者信心，为资本流入奠定基础，并支撑汇丰控股有限公司对该国资产的看涨立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/turkey-s-orthodox-pivot-makes-lira-a-favorite-for-hsbc</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 10:33:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国债拍卖创历史新高，全球债券下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/-impressive-demand-for-treasuries-sets-stage-for-next-big-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者准备迎接另一场创纪录规模的美国国债拍卖，消化了可能阻止世界某些地区央行降息的通胀数据，美国国债和其他政府债券暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/-impressive-demand-for-treasuries-sets-stage-for-next-big-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员等待关键通胀数据以获取利率线索，金价保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/gold-xauusd-steady-after-two-day-drop-driven-by-easing-mideast-tension</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黄金在连续两天下跌后于周三交投稳定，因交易员等待本周晚些时候公布的美国关键通胀数据，该数据可能为美联储的利率路径提供更多线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/gold-xauusd-steady-after-two-day-drop-driven-by-easing-mideast-tension</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 00:55:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国债收益率在创纪录的 700 亿美元出售前攀升：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的债券市场面临压力，华尔街正准备再次大规模出售美国国债，这将有助于确定今年的抛售之后是否会出现转折点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 22:58:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>殷拓集团下调销售指导，并计划在 5 月之前削减产量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/eqt-cuts-sales-guidance-plans-to-curtail-production-through-may</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于需求疲软，价格徘徊在四年来的低点附近，美国最大的天然气生产商殷拓集团 (EQT Corp.) 目前正在减产至 5 月份。该公司还下调了 2024 年的销售指引。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/eqt-cuts-sales-guidance-plans-to-curtail-production-through-may</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 21:21:05 GMT</pubDate>
